⚡️Linki: Project Report

 Linki is getting new features and improvements every week, and we want to keep you updated on all the developments. Here is a fresh portion of Linki news.

We have launched the alpha/MVP version of Linki, available to the closed-testing phase participants, who provide their valuable suggestions.
Here are the features which we have already implemented:

🟣Registration and onboarding;
🟣Dashboard interfaces;
🟣Project placement and project manager selection;
🟣Request processing and offer preparation;
🟣Team formation and networking;
🟣Notifications and Telegram chat integration;
🟣Referral program;
🟣Closed and open connections;
🟣Payment gateway integration.

We are working on the Safe Deal feature, developing the iOS and Android apps, preparing the ranking system, and testing user behavior scenarios.

We've scheduled the launch for November, and our main goal is to roll out a product that will be convenient, easy-to-navigate, and free of bugs. And since there are already a few dozen pre-registrations on Linki, we've decided to first release it in the closed testing mode for a limited number of users.#freelance #freelanceplatform #freelancing #digitalart #digitalmarketing #projectmanagement #motiondesign #motiondesignerscommunity #motiondesigner #motionsesigners #motiondesignworld #fintech #fintechday #IT #graphicdesign #startups #startupdaily

